**$1,500–$5,000 — [Point Up Pear Lab 3 ct in 14K Yellow Gold at $2,292.](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/point-up-pear-cut-lab-grown-diamond-solitaire-pendant-in-14k-yellow-gold-3-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251327?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** The size-per-dollar winner of the entire guide. A 3 ct natural pear pendant at this grade costs $25,000+. This is $2,292.

